						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone standing in front of the Hanumān temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1307.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1229, Plavaṅga, Bhādrapada, Amāvāsyā, Monday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1307, August 28,</hi> the month being adhika-Bhādrapada.</p>						

						<p>This inscription records a gift of land to <hi rend="italic">mahāprabhu</hi> Kēśavadēva by Haridēva Rāṇeya.</p>						

