<p>
<lb n="1"/>© svasti śrī 1229 palavaṁga saṁ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vacharada bhādrapada ba sōmavāra
<lb n="3"/>Āmāseli śrīkaraṇādhipati mahādē
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vapaṁḍitara ma<unclear>li</unclear>hanta haridēvarāṇeya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ru sa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> geya mahāprabhu
<lb n="6"/>kēsavadēvaṁge teṁkaṇa holadali muli
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ga<unclear>rasa</unclear> muḍadeseya sīme teṁka<unclear>de</unclear>seya
<lb n="8" break="no"/>li cikkamosaḷeya sīme paḍuvadeseya
<lb n="9" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> geya <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> sīme baḍagadeseya
<lb n="10" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> diya nāgu<unclear>ha</unclear>narā sīme yiṁtī ca
<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> paḍada keyanu dhārāpūrvvaka
<lb n="12" break="no"/><ce>damaged</ce>
<lb n="13"/>ṁ koṭṭaru maṁgaḷa mahā śrī śrī
